===Ecology===
According to the [[A. W. Kuchler]] U.S. [[Potential natural vegetation]] Types, Hartsel would have a [[Wheatgrass]] / [[Needlegrass]] (''66'') vegetation type and a North [[Mixed grass prairie]] (''7'') vegetation form.<ref name="Conservation Biology Institute">{{cite web|url=https://databasin.org/datasets/1c7a301c8e6843f2b4fe63fdb3a9fe39|publisher=[[Data Basin]]|accessdate=2019-07-11|title=U.S. Potential Natural Vegetation, Original Kuchler Types, v2.0 (Spatially Adjusted to Correct Geometric Distortions)}}</ref>

